
## ⚙️ Installation Steps

### 1. Clone Repository

```bash
git clone https://github.com/yourusername/Secure-Login-System.git
2. Open Project Folder
cd Secure-Login-System
3. Install Dependencies
pip install -r requirements.txt
4. Run Application
python app.py
5. Open Browser
http://127.0.0.1:5000
